sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Thanos as Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 1: User Accesses Dashboard UI

    Browser->>Router: GET /dashboard<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS
    Router->>OAuth: TLS Reencrypt<br/>HTTPS/8443
    OAuth->>OAuth: Check OAuth session cookie
    alt No valid session
        OAuth-->>Browser: 302 Redirect to OpenShift OAuth
        Browser->>OAuth: OAuth callback with auth code
        OAuth->>OAuth: Set session cookie (23h expiry)
    end
    OAuth->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token header
    Backend-->>OAuth: Static assets (React SPA)
    OAuth-->>Router: Response (TLS)
    Router-->>Browser: HTML/JS/CSS

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Notebook Start/Stop

    Browser->>Router: POST /api/notebooks<br/>HTTPS/443
    Router->>OAuth: TLS Reencrypt/8443
    OAuth->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>OAuth forwarded token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: CREATE/PATCH kubeflow.org/Notebook<br/>HTTPS/443, User Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Notebook CR response
    Backend-->>Browser: Notebook status

    Note over Browser,Thanos: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Query

    Browser->>Router: POST /api/prometheus/pvc<br/>HTTPS/443
    Router->>OAuth: TLS Reencrypt/8443
    OAuth->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>OAuth forwarded token
    Backend->>Thanos: PromQL query<br/>HTTPS/9092, User Bearer Token
    Thanos-->>Backend: Metric results
    Backend-->>Browser: JSON metrics

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 4: K8s API Pass-through

    Browser->>Router: GET /api/k8s/apis/...<br/>HTTPS/443
    Router->>OAuth: TLS Reencrypt/8443
    OAuth->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>OAuth forwarded token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Proxied API request<br/>HTTPS/443, User Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: K8s API response
    Backend-->>Browser: JSON response

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 5: WebSocket K8s Watch

    Browser->>Router: WS /wss/k8s/*<br/>HTTPS/443
    Router->>OAuth: TLS Reencrypt/8443
    OAuth->>Backend: WS/8080<br/>K8s bearer token subprotocol
    Backend->>K8sAPI: WSS/443<br/>base64url.bearer.authorization.k8s.io
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Watch events (streaming)
    Backend-->>Browser: Resource change events
